reviewText:
I just received this package (3/25).  This DVD was sealed with the necessary stickers on the openings and the plastic covering the DVD.  When I opened it the DVD was missing! What is my next step to either getting this replaced or a refund?

Please advise.
It was not what I had expected, just a bunch of porn stars doing not so porn stuff, very uninteresting!
Thank you for asking me to rate this, but I have no recollection of receiving it.  that means you never sent it or I threw it away as soon as I had a quick look at it.
peach movies are all the same not bad but not awfull but not the best either same girl in three different movies
